title: Heath's Natural Foods
description: Provides selections in fresh organic foods, produce, and health foods since 1970. Also a juice bar and deli serving fresh juices, soups, fair trade coffee, wheat grass juice, prepared wraps, salads, pates, salsa, guacamole, hummus, party trays and more all made from organic ingredients. Sells organic wines from around the world and gluten-free beers. NOTE: They will soon break ground for an addition which will allow more beer, wine, grab and go selections and more gourmet foods.
